		"description": "<p>Even a chaotic mess can be made useful using prisimancy. You flood the area around yourself with multicolored pigments and each creature (except you) in a 35-foot cube centered on you must make a Dexterity saving throw. For each target, roll a d8 to determine which color of pigment affects it.</p>\n<table style=\"width: 99.596%; height: 302.344px;\" border=\"1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 8.95105%;\"><col style=\"width: 22.0137%;\"><col style=\"width: 69.0535%;\"></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 33.5938px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 33.5938px; text-align: center;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"height: 33.5938px; text-align: center;\">Red</td>\n<td style=\"height: 33.5938px;\">The target takes 6d6 fire damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 33.5938px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 33.5938px; text-align: center;\">2</td>\n<td style=\"height: 33.5938px; text-align: center;\">Orange</td>\n<td style=\"height: 33.5938px;\">The target takes 6d6 acid damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 33.5938px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 33.5938px; text-align: center;\">3</td>\n<td style=\"height: 33.5938px; text-align: center;\">Yellow</td>\n<td style=\"height: 33.5938px;\">The target takes 6d6 lightning damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 33.5938px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 33.5938px; text-align: center;\">4</td>\n<td style=\"height: 33.5938px; text-align: center;\">Green</td>\n<td style=\"height: 33.5938px;\">&nbsp;The target takes 6d6 poison damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 33.5938px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 33.5938px; text-align: center;\">5</td>\n<td style=\"height: 33.5938px; text-align: center;\">Blue</td>\n<td style=\"height: 33.5938px;\">The target takes 6d6 cold damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 67.1875px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 67.1875px; text-align: center;\">6</td>\n<td style=\"height: 67.1875px; text-align: center;\">Indigo</td>\n<td style=\"height: 67.1875px;\">On a failed save, the target is&nbsp;<span class=\"freelinking-link\">restrained</span>&nbsp;. It must make a Strength&nbsp;<span class=\"freelinking-link\">saving throw</span>&nbsp;at the end of each of its turns. On a successful saving throw it frees itself from the constricting pigments and is no longer restrained.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 50.3906px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 50.3906px; text-align: center;\">7</td>\n<td style=\"height: 50.3906px; text-align: center;\">Violet</td>\n<td style=\"height: 50.3906px;\">On a failed save, the target is&nbsp;<span class=\"freelinking-link\">blinded</span>&nbsp;. At the start of each of the creature&rsquo;s turns, it makes a Constitution&nbsp;<span class=\"freelinking-link\">saving throw</span>&nbsp;, ending the effect on itself on a success.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 16.7969px; text-align: center;\">8</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.7969px; text-align: center;\">Special</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">The target is afflicted by two pigments. Roll twice more, rerolling any 8.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",
